{"data":[{"date":"09:50 16/07","title":"Mourinho mong m\u1ecfi sao s\u00e1ng Croatia s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/mourinho-len-tieng-hy-vong-sao-sang-croatia-se-gia-nhap-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Ivan Perisic trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ivan Perisic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ivan Perisic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-HLV-Mourinho-muon-MU-chieu-mo-Ivan-Perisic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Perisic l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t VCK World Cup 2018 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Croatia. Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 anh t\u1eeb Inter Milan. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh Russia Today, HLV Mourinho v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ivan Perisic, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 anh v\u1eeba gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ivan Perisic? Anh \u1ea5y \u0111i t\u1eeb Croatia \u0111\u1ebfn Borussia, Dortmund, Wolfburg r\u1ed3i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Inter Milan.\u00a0T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao Perisic l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn Man United khi t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n anh \u1ea5y\",\u00a0HLV Mourinho chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, Mourinho c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc l\u1eddi khen n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Perisic: \u201cPerisic l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t th\u1ea3y. Nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t quen thu\u1ed9c m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta hay n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean gi\u1ecfi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng Perisic th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00f3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. V\u00f4 c\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. V\u00e0 Perisic c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn n\u1eefa. C\u00e1ch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e8 r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng cho Mario Mandzukic ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Inter. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau World Cup 2018, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y cho Perisic.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh \u0111\u01b0a tin, ph\u00eda M.U mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng (50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) c\u1ee7a 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia Matteo Darmian cho Inter \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Perisic ngay trong H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh-421-191201.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh-421-191201.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e9p v\u1ebf v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng Ba tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U Roy Keane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester-172-191192.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester-172-191192.html\">Th\u00eam b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y M.U s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 M.U.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/gareth-bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-real-ve-voi-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\">M.U \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201csao b\u1ef1\u201d Real</span><br>\r\nSau khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus, Real Madrid l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi n\u1ed7i lo m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao n\u1eefa. Th\u00f4ng tin MU \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh mua Gareth...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1312","checkdouble":"191324"},{"date":"10:13 16/07","title":"Ibrahimovic khen Pogba sau danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Zlatan Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho Pogba sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Croatia \u0111\u00eam qua.</h2><h2>Ibra khen ng\u1ee3i Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p trong hi\u1ec7p hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia. V\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t d\u1eadp t\u1eaft tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Vatreni.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Pogba tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Balkan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibrahimovic khen Pogba sau danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ibrahimovic khen Pogba sau danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ibrahimovic khen Pogba tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00f3i thay t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\u201d, Ibrahimovic chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u00f4m chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nPogba v\u00e0 Ibrahimovic l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17. Nh\u1edd hai ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y, Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi 3 danh hi\u1ec7u. Nh\u01b0ng sau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Lukaku, Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn LA Galaxy v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, Pogba ch\u01a1i l\u0103n x\u1ea3 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 h\u00f4m qua l\u00e0 Croatia \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Pogba t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 4 l\u1ea7n, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 Kante. S\u1ea3i ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Pogba khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00e0 khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Lloris nh\u1edd v\u1eady c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n trong kh\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Pogba c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng. Anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e2ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-1 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p ch\u01a1i th\u1ea3nh th\u1eddi h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/cdv-phap-phan-khich-va-qua-khich-an-mung-doi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-461-191328.html\">C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nong-tien-ve-pogba-hat-its-coming-home-che-nhao-nuoc-anh-421-191310.html\">N\u00d3NG: Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba h\u00e1t It's coming home ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1311","checkdouble":"191326"},{"date":"09:39 16/07","title":"C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/cdv-phap-phan-khich-va-qua-khich-an-mung-doi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.</h2><h2>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi chu\u1ed1i 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a CLB SLNA</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng, CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd khi gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 21 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 4 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m t\u1ed1p 3 \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi SLNA to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi SLNA to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/HLV-Nguyen-Duc-Thang-bi-soc-khi-SLNA-toan-thang-7-tran-lien-tiep-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SLNA</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 NHM h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ngay c\u1ea3 HLV SLNA, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1eebng su\u00fdt t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c SLNA cho hay: \u201cT\u00f4i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a SLNA. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1eeba qua. Ti\u00eau ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh, ni\u1ec1m vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng nhau s\u1ebb chia\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cTrong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, sai s\u00f3t hay c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung, lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m\u201d. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, SLNA s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm l\u00e0 HAGL. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n, k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\">SLNA 2-1 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam (KT): Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ee9 7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Th\u1eafng v\u00e0 Olaha, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i to\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu-168-189826.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu-168-189826.html\">Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1310","checkdouble":"191328"},{"date":"10:04 16/07","title":"C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/canh-sat-paris-dung-do-cdv-qua-khich-sau-khi-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1eeb m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng sau khi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00e1 ho\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea5n \u00e1p.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/croatia-nhung-nguoi-viet-nen-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia (Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nCroatia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup khi thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh nh\u00ecn Les Bleus l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-2 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Ph\u00e1p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u00e2n Luzhniki \u0103n m\u1eebng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 tr\u00ean to\u00e0n n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0103n m\u1eebng l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai Les Bleus \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/canh-sat-paris-dung-do-cdv-qua-khich-sau-khi-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 Champs-Elysees \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf n\u00ean k\u00e9m vui khi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng g\u00e2y r\u1ed1i. H\u1ecd n\u00e9m \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o c\u00e1c c\u1eeda k\u00ednh quanh \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 Champs-Elysees.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sky Sports, kho\u1ea3ng 30 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111eo m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 lao v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u01b0\u1edbp r\u01b0\u1ee3u. C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t ch\u1ed1ng b\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng Paris bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i t\u00e1n nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch b\u1eb1ng s\u00fang n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 h\u01a1i cay. \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 danh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris ch\u1ec9 d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ebb b\u00ecnh y\u00ean v\u00e0o 11h30 \u0111\u00eam (theo gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ed5 ra \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u n\u01a1i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Paris, nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u1ea3nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 khi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u g\u00e2y r\u1ed1i. Theo c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Lyon x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t v\u00e0 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 khi g\u1ea7n 100 thanh thi\u1ebfu ni\u00ean c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh leo l\u00ean m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe c\u1ee9u h\u1ecfa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ea1n kh\u00ed cay \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i t\u00e1n nh\u1eefng thanh ni\u00ean k\u00edch \u0111\u1ed9ng khi h\u1ecd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed1t l\u1eeda v\u00e0 n\u00e9m c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1eadt v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng an ninh. \u1ede Marseille, 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00e0 2 c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/16/French-cops-deploy-tear-gas-&-water-cannons-to-contain-fan-frenzy-after-World-Cup-win-()---RT.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/16/Police-and-football-fans-clash-in-Paris-after-France\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/cdv-phap-phan-khich-va-qua-khich-an-mung-doi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-461-191328.html\">C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tuyen-phap-quay-tung-phong-hop-bao-sau-chuc-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-461-191325.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p qu\u1eady t\u01b0ng ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-nhan-gui-real-madrid-sau-khi-vo-dich-world-cup-421-191317.html\">Mbappe nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi Real Madrid sau khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-nghi-sao-khi-chau-phi-vo-dich-world-cup-khong-phai-phap-421-191315.html\">Griezmann ngh\u0129 sao khi Ch\u00e2u Phi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nong-tien-ve-pogba-hat-its-coming-home-che-nhao-nuoc-anh-421-191310.html\">N\u00d3NG: Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba h\u00e1t It's coming home ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gianh-chuc-vo-dich-varane-di-vao-lich-su-421-191308.html\">Gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Varane s\u00e1nh ngang Beckenbauer v\u00e0 Carlos</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1309","checkdouble":"191330"},{"date":"10:08 16/07","title":"\u0110\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/danh-roi-chien-thang-truoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 'k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u' \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 15/7, CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 t\u1edbi Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 g\u1eb7p CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC l\u00e0 c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn l\u00e0 v\u1eady song c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn khi ghi t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Diogo v\u00e0 Th\u1ebf V\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp g\u1ee1 l\u1ea1i 3 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ebd m\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Van Sy\" title=\"HLV V\u0103n S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/danh-roi-chien-thang-truoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc khi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ecb H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 3-3</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 n\u00f3i: &ldquo;C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i qu\u00e1 non n\u1edbt, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi nh\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t r\u1ed3i, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1n theo nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u00e2u b\u00f3ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00eam cho c\u00e1c em. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 thua. G\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, t\u00e2m l\u00fd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00e0ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 s\u1ec7t k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi thua tr\u1eadn&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng S\u1ef9 c\u0169ng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eb7n l\u1ed9i m\u01b0a gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng con c\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 v\u00e0 C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. H\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, v\u00ec b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00e0 l\u00e0 v\u00ec t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3&rdquo;, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i gi\u00fap Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng khi h\u01a1n S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191252.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191252.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 3-3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (KT): D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day-291-191271.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day.JPEG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day-291-191271.html\">C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng ngay t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby</span><br>\r\nC\u01a1n m\u01b0a t\u1ea7m t\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m v\u01a1i \u0111i s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League, C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i, trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1308","checkdouble":"191331"},{"date":"10:26 16/07","title":"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi SLNA to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/slna-toan-thang-7-tran-lien-tiep-hlv-nguyen-duc-thang-bi-soc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.</h2><h2>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi chu\u1ed1i 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a CLB SLNA</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng, CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd khi gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 21 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 4 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m t\u1ed1p 3 \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi SLNA to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi SLNA to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/HLV-Nguyen-Duc-Thang-bi-soc-khi-SLNA-toan-thang-7-tran-lien-tiep-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SLNA</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 NHM h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ngay c\u1ea3 HLV SLNA, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1eebng su\u00fdt t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c SLNA cho hay: \u201cT\u00f4i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a SLNA. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1eeba qua. Ti\u00eau ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh, ni\u1ec1m vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng nhau s\u1ebb chia\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cTrong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, sai s\u00f3t hay c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung, lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m\u201d. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, SLNA s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm l\u00e0 HAGL. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n, k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\">SLNA 2-1 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam (KT): Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ee9 7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Th\u1eafng v\u00e0 Olaha, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i to\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu-168-189826.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu-168-189826.html\">Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1307","checkdouble":"191332"},{"date":"11:11 16/07","title":"Deschamps: \"Mbappe c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/deschamps-mbappe-co-the-vo-dich-world-cup-mot-lan-nua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Didier Deschamps tin r\u1eb1ng Mbappe ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa khi m\u00e0 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb.</h2><h2>Deschamps \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Mbappe\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Deschamps \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Mbappe sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Deschamps \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Mbappe sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/deschamps-mbappe-co-the-vo-dich-world-cup-mot-lan-nua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Deschamps \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Mbappe sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\" target=\"_blank\">chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span>. Anh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb th\u1ee9 hai sau Pele l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. V\u00e0 HLV Deschamps cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng hy v\u1ecdng sao tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd c\u00f2n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01a1n th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMbappe m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 19 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb s\u1edbm. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 20 n\u0103m, Trezeguet v\u00e0 Henry kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa cho d\u00f9 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u0103ng quang khi c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Deschamps khen b\u1ed9 ba tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng hay kh\u00f4ng. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng ca ng\u1ee3i ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i li\u00ean h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa Griezmann, Mbappe v\u00e0 Pogba \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cGriezmann l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Mbappe, Pogba hay Griezmann. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng lu\u00f4n nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f9ng nhau. \u0110\u00f4i khi c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng xung \u0111\u1ed9t. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u1eafng nghe tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. Sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. V\u00e0 h\u00f4m nay, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Ph\u00e1p:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-an-tuong-khong-the-dong-dem-421-191297.html\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018: \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111ong \u0111\u1ebfm</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191296.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1306","checkdouble":"191333"},{"date":"11:28 16/07","title":"H\u1eadu chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng v\u00e0 k\u1ebb thua \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/hau-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-nguoi-thang-va-ke-thua-deu-do-ra-duong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 qua v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a mang t\u00ednh bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 th\u1eafng hay thua, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t qu\u1ed1c gia, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/croatia-nhung-nguoi-viet-nen-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia (Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nCroatia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup khi thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh nh\u00ecn Les Bleus l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 b\u1ed1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Croatia \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp hay gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c Phi. 15/23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c t\u1eeb l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba \u0111en, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i Kylian Mbappe.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 Khi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 anh em h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 Khi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 anh em h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Hau-chung-ket-World-Cup-2018-Khi-tat-ca-deu-la-anh-em-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>15 trong s\u1ed1 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 g\u1ed1c ch\u00e2u Phi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eb3ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn ni\u1ec1m vui c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<strong> </strong></div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p!</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 Champs-Elysees (Paris) \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i. Bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ed1c Phi th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 th\u1ee9 hai, th\u1ee9 ba,... tr\u00ean l\u00e3nh th\u1ed5 Ph\u00e1p. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Goffrey Hamsik (Paris) m\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10, s\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Kylian Mbappe c\u00f9ng chi\u1ebfc m\u0169 g\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng - bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p - h\u00e2n hoan n\u00f3i: &quot;Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a l\u1edbn lao. N\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tinh th\u1ea7n. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nhau, h\u00f2a tr\u1ed9n v\u1edbi nhau. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u00f4n gi\u00e1o, s\u1eafc t\u1ed9c, kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec c\u1ea3, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nguoi dan Phap do ra duong an mung sau tran chung ket World Cup 2018.\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0103n m\u1eebng sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/ck-wc-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0103n m\u1eebng sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u1ea5n c\u1edd l\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi, \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc m\u0169 g\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng hay r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u h\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb kh\u00e1c. \u1ede Paris, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 Champs-Elysees, n\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p th\u01b0\u1eddng di\u1ec5u binh trong ng\u00e0y Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00e1nh, hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y Bastille.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 danh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Paris ng\u1eadp trong bom kh\u00f3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1eafc xanh, \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 tr\u1eafng. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi leo l\u00ean c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 b\u00e1o, \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ee3i xe bu\u00fdt hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 n\u01a1i n\u00e0o cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eaby c\u1edd, k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111o\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0103n m\u1eebng. Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca c\u1ee7a &quot;La Marseillaise&quot; (qu\u1ed1c ca Ph\u00e1p) vang l\u00ean kh\u1eafp ch\u1ed1n.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t ch\u1ed1ng b\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec3n khai m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng sau m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n \u0103n m\u1eebng, c\u1eeda k\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng hay b\u1ecb n\u00e9m v\u1ee1, nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 kh\u00e1c b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y. Kho\u1ea3ng 4.000 c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec3n khai \u1edf khu &quot;Fan zone&quot;, n\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ebfn 90.000 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn t\u1ed1i, t\u00f2a th\u00e1p Eiffel nh\u00e1y l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 1998-2018 bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0ng cho hai l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Kh\u1ea3i Ho\u00e0n M\u00f4n t\u1eafm trong m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a c\u1edd Ph\u00e1p, chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng in l\u00ean h\u00ecnh ch\u00fa g\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef &quot;T\u1ef1 h\u00e0o s\u1eafc xanh&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chien thang tai World Cup 2018 lam nguoi Phap tro nen doan ket hon.\" title=\"Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft h\u01a1n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/ck-wc-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft h\u01a1n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac l\u1eafm. 20 n\u0103m r\u1ed3i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y g\u1eafn k\u1ebft m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi&quot; - Frederique Pourquet c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 Champs-Elysees cho \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1i. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng qu\u00e1n bar \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng ni\u1ec1m vui n\u00e0y h\u1ebft \u0111\u00eam.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Omar Bzi, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V kh\u00e1c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &quot;Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 cho n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p&quot;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hajar Maghnaoui \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Asnieres, ph\u00eda B\u1eafc Paris n\u00f3i: &quot;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n nhau, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n \u1edf Croatia, b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed tr\u1ea7m l\u1eafng h\u01a1n \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed \u1edf Zagreb (Croatia) tr\u1ea7m l\u1eafng h\u01a1n \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat. S\u1ef1 \u1ed3n \u00e0o, h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Croatia. C\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0 ng\u1eebng l\u1ea1i khi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft di\u1ec5n ra, c\u00f2n gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng g\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 thao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac CDV Croatia du buon nhung van tu hao sau tran chung ket World Cup 2018.\" title=\"C\u00e1c C\u0110V Croatia d\u00f9 bu\u1ed3n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/ck-wc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c C\u0110V Croatia d\u00f9 bu\u1ed3n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Croatia l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng&quot; - C\u1ed5ng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed Index \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i: &quot;\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft c\u1ea3 qu\u1ed1c gia&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u1edf th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Zagreb m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n, ho\u1eb7c kho\u00e1c l\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1 c\u1edd t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ed3 ra c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 tuy\u1ebfn ph\u1ed1 v\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft \u0111\u00eam. Nh\u01b0ng khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, ch\u1eb3ng ai gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o b\u1edfi ch\u1eb3ng ai ngh\u0129 Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 cho \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Aleksandar Todorovic (Zagreb) n\u00f3i: &quot;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00f4i bu\u1ed3n khi ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p n\u00e2ng c\u00fap. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia v\u1eabn v\u1eaby c\u1edd v\u00e0 h\u00e1t l\u00ean nh\u1eefng giai \u0111i\u1ec7u t\u1ef1 h\u00e0i, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t tinh th\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u, h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5u h\u00e0nh qua c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn ph\u1ed1 t\u1edbi qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00ednh \u1edf Zagreb. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1eabn n\u00e1n l\u1ea1i cho \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1i mu\u1ed9n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric va nguoi Croatia van co the tu hao du that bai trong tran chung ket World Cup 2018.\" title=\"Luka Modric v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o d\u00f9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/modric-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Luka Modric v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o d\u00f9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 t\u01b0\u1edbng Croata, Andrej Plenkovic n\u00f3i: &quot;M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00ean l\u00e0m. \u0110\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u v\u1edbi Croatia v\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 sao \u0111i n\u1eefa, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e3nh di\u1ec7n khi Luka Modric, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn cho nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a Modric, m\u00e0 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 &quot;Vatreni&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sofia Halinovcic (26 tu\u1ed5i) n\u00f3i: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eebng l\u00e0m. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111ang l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng&quot;.<br>\r\n<em> </em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>* Theo ESPN.</em><strong> </strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/deschamps-mbappe-co-the-vo-dich-world-cup-mot-lan-nua-469-191333.html\">Deschamps: Mbappe c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/canh-sat-paris-dung-do-cdv-qua-khich-sau-khi-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-465-191330.html\">C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/cdv-phap-phan-khich-va-qua-khich-an-mung-doi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-461-191328.html\">C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tuyen-phap-quay-tung-phong-hop-bao-sau-chuc-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-461-191325.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p qu\u1eady t\u01b0ng ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/video-hazard-quay-tung-bung-khi-tro-ve-bi-421-191314.html\">Video: Hazard qu\u1ea9y t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nong-tien-ve-pogba-hat-its-coming-home-che-nhao-nuoc-anh-421-191310.html\">N\u00d3NG: Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba h\u00e1t It's coming home ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1305","checkdouble":"191335"},{"date":"11:50 16/07","title":"V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb FIFA?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/vo-dich-world-cup-2018-phap-duoc-nhan-bao-nhieu-tien-tu-fifa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb FIFA v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018? Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 g\u1ea5p 4 l\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/croatia-nhung-nguoi-viet-nen-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia (Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup khi thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh nh\u00ecn Les Bleus l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb FIFA?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a l\u1edbn lao v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tinh th\u1ea7n, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb FIFA.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb FIFA h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb FIFA h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/vo-dich-world-cup-2018-phap-duoc-nhan-bao-nhieu-tien-tu-fifa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn 38 tri\u1ec7u USD nh\u1edd ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo FIFA c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i, kho\u1ea3ng 400 tri\u1ec7u USD (\u0111\u00f4 la M\u1ef9) s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1edfng cho th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Trong \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 38 tri\u1ec7u USD.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn bao nhi\u00eau?<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0110T Croatia kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e2ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng m\u00e0 m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn 10 tri\u1ec7u USD ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng. FIFA trao m\u1ee9c th\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 28 tri\u1ec7u USD, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng sau l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn 24 tri\u1ec7u USD trong khi \u0110T Anh nh\u1eadn 22 tri\u1ec7u USD. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u00e0 Uruguay, Brazil, Nga v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f9ng nh\u1eadn 16 tri\u1ec7u USD. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 l\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, Argentina, Mexico, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, Colombia chung m\u1ee9c 12 tri\u1ec7u USD.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 t\u1eeb sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn 8 tri\u1ec7u USD, b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n t\u01b0 so v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i \u1ea2 R\u1eadp X\u00ea \u00dat, Ai C\u1eadp, Iran, Ma R\u1ed1c, Peru, Australia, Nigeria, Iceland, Serbia, Costa Rica, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110\u1ee9c, Tunisia, Panama, Senegal, Ba Lan.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hau-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-nguoi-thang-va-ke-thua-deu-do-ra-duong-465-191335.html\">H\u1eadu chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng v\u00e0 k\u1ebb thua \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/canh-sat-paris-dung-do-cdv-qua-khich-sau-khi-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-465-191330.html\">C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Paris \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/cdv-phap-phan-khich-va-qua-khich-an-mung-doi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-461-191328.html\">C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tuyen-phap-quay-tung-phong-hop-bao-sau-chuc-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-461-191325.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p qu\u1eady t\u01b0ng ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/video-hazard-quay-tung-bung-khi-tro-ve-bi-421-191314.html\">Video: Hazard qu\u1ea9y t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-cdv-chay-vao-san-trong-tran-chung-ket-phap-vs-croatia-la-ai-421-191307.html\">C\u00e1c C\u0110V ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia l\u00e0 ai?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1304","checkdouble":"191336"},{"date":"11:50 16/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 16/7: Tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean M.U quan t\u00e2m ai \u1edf tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/ngay-hom-nay-167.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (16/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>Tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean M.U quan t\u00e2m ai \u1edf tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ph\u00eda Manchester United \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn xem tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Croatia v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u1eafm ng\u00eda 3 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ec1u thu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Croatia g\u1ed3m Ivan Perisic, Mario Mandzukic v\u00e0 Sime Vrsaljko. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, Ivan Perisic c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Old Trafford b\u1edfi Man United su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a anh trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 167, tin n\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 167, tin n\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/z-1917.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi Inter Milan, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Perisic \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ee1 trong ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Perisic ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u BL\u0110 Man United nhanh ch\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Perisic th\u00eam l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Mario Mandzukic d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u trung phong c\u1eafm \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh m\u00e0 Mourinho kh\u00e1 \u01b0a th\u00edch. Mandzukic s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chia l\u1eeda v\u1edbi Lukaku tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Sime Vrsaljko, n\u0103m nay 26 tu\u1ed5i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u1ea3 vai tr\u00f2 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i l\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i - v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri, Chelsea c\u00f2n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Jorginho. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Loftus-Cheek b\u1ecb \u0111e d\u1ecda. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Loftus-Cheek ch\u01a1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh. Theo Daily Mail, Arsenal c\u1ee7a HLV Emery \u0111ang \u00e2m m\u01b0u \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn Emirates, thay th\u1ebf Jack Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois \u1ee1m \u1edd v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Thiabaut Courtois v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. V\u1eeba k\u1ebft th\u00fac h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ec9, Courtois \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1edbi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eb1ng anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Courtois \u0111ang r\u1ee7 r\u00ea Hazard \u0111\u1ebfn Real c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-191268.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, Courtois \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng \u201cv\u00f2i v\u0129nh\u201d Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Trippier</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Kieran Trippier g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh. B\u00e1m bi\u00ean t\u1ed1t, t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh chu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n Trippier \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Liverpool, Man City hay MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Tottenham ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Trippier ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f3n Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3n HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ee5c r\u1ecbch tri\u1ec3n khai k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Gonzalo Higuain. Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Italia, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho El Pipita, k\u00e8m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 7,5 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-juventus-172-191164.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-juventus.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-juventus-172-191164.html\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n v\u1edbi Juventus</span><br>\r\n<span>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Alvaro Morata l\u1ea5y Gonzalo Higuain, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ferdinand th\u00fac M.U mua Mbappe</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Croatia, Rio Ferdinand ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Anh hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Man Utd s\u1ebd ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1303","checkdouble":"191337"},{"date":"07:42 16/07","title":"Gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Varane s\u00e1nh ngang Beckenbauer v\u00e0 Carlos","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/gianh-chuc-vo-dich-varane-di-vao-lich-su.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Raphael Varane l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nVarane \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 4-2 d\u00e0nh cho \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois \u0111em chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch tr\u00f2n 20 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc &ndash; m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Raphael Varane, danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a l\u1edbn h\u01a1n th\u1ebf, khi anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (Champions League/ Europa League) l\u1eabn World Cup trong v\u00f2ng 1 n\u0103m. Trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 9 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Varane l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Varane l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/gianh-chuc-vo-dich-varane-di-vao-lich-su.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Varane l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Varane \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i CLB, c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap C1 l\u00e0 Luka Modric. Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, Varane kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic, b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div>\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Sami Khedira, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u00e0 World Cup 2014 &ndash; nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong l\u00fac kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br>\r\n</span></span></div>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"width:100.0%;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;&#10; mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"100%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:100.0%;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;background:#FFFFCC;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><br>\r\n            D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh   s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap <strong>c\u00fap</strong>&nbsp;<strong>ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 World Cup</strong> trong 1 n\u0103m (\u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n l\u00e0 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ea3   2 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng):<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">1974: Sepp Maier,   Paul Breitner, Hans-Georg Schwarzenbeck, Franz Beckenbauer, Gerd Muller, Uli   Hoeness (Bayern &amp; T\u00e2y \u0110\u1ee9c)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-