;line-height:normal\">1988: Hans van   Breukelen, Ronald Koeman, Berry van Aerle, Gerald Vanenburg (PSV Eindhoven   &amp; H\u00e0 Lan)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">2012: Fernando   Torres, Juan Mata (Chelsea &amp; T\u00e2y Ban Nha)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">2016: Cristiano   Ronaldo, Pepe (Real Madrid &amp; B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha)<br>\r\n            &nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span></span>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-cdv-chay-vao-san-trong-tran-chung-ket-phap-vs-croatia-la-ai-421-191307.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/cac-cdv-chay-vao-san-trong-tran-chung-ket-phap-vs-croatia-la-ai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-cdv-chay-vao-san-trong-tran-chung-ket-phap-vs-croatia-la-ai-421-191307.html\">C\u00e1c C\u0110V ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia l\u00e0 ai?</span><br>\r\nTrong hi\u1ec7p 2 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ecb gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n \u00edt ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/khong-phai-mbappe-day-moi-la-cau-thu-chay-nhanh-nhat-world-cup-421-191304.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/khong-phai-mbappe-day-moi-la-cau-thu-chay-nhanh-nhat-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/khong-phai-mbappe-day-moi-la-cau-thu-chay-nhanh-nhat-world-cup-421-191304.html\"