dbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 chung cu\u1ed9c, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i DJ khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nHazard &ldquo;c\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ea7u&rdquo; \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110T Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3, kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thomas Meunier v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Eden Hazard l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n \u1edf Qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng anh h\u00f9ng d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c, sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i DJ sau khi x\u00e1ch vali v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hazard tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i DJ sau khi x\u00e1ch vali v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/haz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i DJ t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Thibaut Courtois, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n nh\u1ea1c s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\" target=\"_blank\">Hazard \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea</span>, khi th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh \u0111ang \u0103n m\u1eebng sau khi tr\u1ea3i qua ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng xem clip Hazard tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i DJ ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/16/in3y8.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-191268.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-191268.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, Courtois \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng &ldquo;v\u00f2i v\u0129nh&rdquo; Chelsea</span><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Anh g\u1ee3i \u00fd r\u1eb1ng The Blues s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-bi-gianh-hang-ba-world-cup-cho-nhe-euro-2020-421-191212.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/dt-bi-gianh-hang-ba-world-cup-cho-nhe-euro-2020.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-bi-gianh-hang-ba-world-cup-cho-nhe-euro-2020-421-191212.html\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng Ba World Cup: Ch\u1edd nh\u00e9 EURO 2020!</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng Ba World Cup n\u0103m nay, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i s\u1eafc n\u00e9t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0n sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. V\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1300","checkdouble":"191314"},{"date":"08:49 16/07","title":"Griezmann ngh\u0129 sao khi \"Ch\u00e2u Phi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Ph\u00e1p\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/griezmann-nghi-sao-khi-chau-phi-vo-dich-world-cup-khong-phai-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng gay g\u1eaft v\u1edbi l\u1eddi ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o, ng\u00f4i sao Atletico Madrid nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n ca ng\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft trong t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-croatia-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-463-191254.html\" target=\"_blank\">Xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-2 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft</span>, Ph\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n anti-fan \u0111\u00e3 tranh th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o, m\u1ec9a mai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng vang d\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a G\u00e0 Tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia (Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann n\u00f3i g\u00ec Ch\u00e2u Phi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Griezmann n\u00f3i g\u00ec Ch\u00e2u Phi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/griezmann-nghi-sao-khi-chau-phi-vo-dich-world-cup-khong-phai-phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c Ch\u00e2u Phi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ch\u00e2m bi\u1ebfm r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup m\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Ch\u00e2u Phi, v\u1edbi nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n do \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Les Bleus bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 da m\u00e0u c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c nh\u1eadp c\u01b0, n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng Paul Pogba, Kylian Mbappe, Raphael Varane hay Samuel Umtiti\u2026<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea5y g\u00ec l\u00e0m vui v\u1ebb v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 m\u00f9i ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griezmann l\u1ea1i v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra \u0111i\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1m v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng gay g\u1eaft m\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4n ngoan nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e2y ca ng\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft trong t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Atletico Madrid sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018: \u201c\u0110\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb m\u1ecdi mi\u1ec1n kh\u00e1c nhau, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00f2ng \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed trong s\u1ed1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n tr\u1eddi xa x\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec quan tr\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi nhau, chia s\u1ebb chung suy ngh\u0129 v\u00e0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u c\u1edd s\u1eafc \u00e1o v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 qu\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-trong-ngay-phap-dang-quang-world-cup-2018-421-191291.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/nhung-diem-nhan-trong-ngay-phap-dang-quang-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-trong-ngay-phap-dang-quang-world-cup-2018-421-191291.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong ng\u00e0y Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. \u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1299","checkdouble":"191315"},{"date":"03:19 16/07","title":"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Antoine Griezmann</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Antoine Griezmann ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. S\u1ed1 7 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, anh ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi 52 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Binh-luan-Phap-vs-Croatia-chung-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Griezmann g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 2 l\u1ea7n, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 1 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Griezmann ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o Lam tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018 (3 b\u00e0n, 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico Madrid cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 ghi 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Ph\u00e1p \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, ch\u1ec9 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n anh cho Les Bleus l\u00e0 Michel Platini (14), Just Fontaine (13) v\u00e0 Thierry Henry (12).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Hugo Lloris</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hugo Lloris \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t anh l\u1ea1i m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lloris co tinh huong xu ly loi\" title=\"Lloris c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1eed l\u00fd l\u1ed7i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/sai.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lloris m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng cho Mandzukic m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 69, t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Samuel Umtiti, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p thay v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng th\u1eadt m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u00ean ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i\u00a0th\u00ec l\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Mario Mandzukic, song ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft b\u00e0i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Mandzukic \u1eadp v\u00e0o qu\u00e1 nhanh khi\u1ebfn Lloris l\u00fang t\u00fang, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Spurs \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u00f3ng bay th\u1eb3ng v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa Lloris l\u1ea1i m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSai l\u1ea7m n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t danh hi\u1ec7u Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 v\u00e0o tay Courtois c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9. R\u1ea5t may cho Lloris l\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Paul Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paul Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, \u1edf tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba dut diem cuc cang nang ty so len 3-1\" title=\"Pogba d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ef1c c\u0103ng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/croatia-nhung-nguoi-viet-nen-lich-su.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U tham gia v\u00e0o m\u1ecdi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, t\u1eeb h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cho \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 6 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0110T Ph\u00e1p (55 l\u1ea7n), anh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 35 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 86%. Pogba c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng, 2 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 gi\u1ea3i nguy k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi, 3 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 1 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-1 cho Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Subasic c\u1ee7a Croatia b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c nh\u00ecn b\u00f3ng bay v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Pogba tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Premier League \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi t\u1eeb Emmanuel Petit v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1998. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang Whoscored ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn. Rio Ferdinand n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Pogba: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p. Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: N'Golo Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, N'Golo Kante \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u1edf World Cup 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n b\u1ebb g\u1eaby nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Kante thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Croatia vs Phap Modric va Kante\" title=\"Croatia vs Phap Modric va Kante\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-Phap-4-2-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Ivan Rakitic v\u00e0 Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho Kante, vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Kante \u0111u\u1ed1i s\u1ee9c, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh anh k\u00e9o ng\u00e3 Ivan Perisic trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111ua t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-phap-42-croatia-421-191293.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia</span> cho th\u1ea5y Kante c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n s\u1ed1 13 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 19 l\u1ea7n, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 54%. Anh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 1 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 1 l\u1ea7n ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng HLV Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat anh ra ngh\u1ec9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o Steven N'Zonzi, c\u1ea7u\u00a0th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao v\u00e0 sung s\u1ee9c h\u01a1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Kylian Mbappe</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup (19 tu\u1ed5i 207 ng\u00e0y), anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 NHM ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe nhan giai thuong cau thu tre xuat sac nhat World Cup 2018\" title=\"Mbappe nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/ki.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Mbappe khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Croatia c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ec7t nho\u00e0i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia. Mbappe l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 Griezmann ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Pogba n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-1 sau \u0111\u00f3 anh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 4-1.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKylian Mbappe (19 tu\u1ed5i 207 ng\u00e0y) l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb th\u1ee9 2 ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup, sau Pele cho Brazil n\u0103m 1958 (17 tu\u1ed5i 249 ng\u00e0y). C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ai x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng h\u01a1n s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u1edf h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Mario Mandzukic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mario Mandzukic l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Anh. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf ph\u00fat 109 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tinh huong Mandzukic phan luoi nha\" title=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Mandzukic ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/Ivan-Rakitic-phat-bieu-ve-tran-chung-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Mandzukic ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 18, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Mandzukic trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. C\u00fa l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 17 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Subasic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Mandzukic gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ung dung tri\u1ec3n khai th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng sau khi d\u1eabn b\u00e0n. D\u00f9 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Hugo Lloris \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 2-4 th\u00ec m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Mandzukic v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMario Mandzukic l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi trong c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, sau Ernie Brandts c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan n\u0103m 1978. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o qu\u00ean v\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 32 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Didier Deschamps</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, HLV Didier Deschamps ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Deschamps phat bieu ve tran Phap vs Croatia\" title=\"HLV Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/des-7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Deschamps g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 49 tu\u1ed5i cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 tinh t\u1ebf v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. Trong khi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn tung h\u1ebft b\u00e0i th\u00ec Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ea9n s\u1ed1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Deschamps c\u0169ng ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 49 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n truy\u1ec1n cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDidier Deschamps tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee9 3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 HLV, sau Mario Zagallo c\u1ee7a Brazil v\u00e0 Franz Beckenbauer c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 20 n\u0103m Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 49 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1298","checkdouble":"191296"}]}